{"tid":2378441,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新華社:腐敗的本質是權力濫用 必須強化對權力運行的制約和監督","createTime":"2021-01-24T12:57:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-24T14:30:35.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"920d4d796fa00a4f472eb4280c35524b209b31dc","tid":2378441,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T12:57:20.000Z","msg":"新華社發表評論員文章，指出十八大以來，黨風廉政建設和反腐敗鬥爭取得歷史性成就，但腐敗這個黨執政的最大風險仍然存在。<br />\n<br />\n文章指出，對於腐敗問題，必須以零容忍的態度、猛藥去疴的決心、刮骨療毒的勇氣，做到有腐必反、有貪必肅，對腐敗形成強大震懾。<br />\n<br />\n文章表示，腐敗的本質是權力濫用，反腐敗鬥爭必須加強制度建設，強化對權力運行的制約和監督。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1572117-20210124.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1572117-20210124.htm&d=phsggM5TdZzYtR7qgPv%2BCIdddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=031654fd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1572117-20210124.htm&h=791d1dba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1572117-20210124.htm</a>"},{"pid":"7e99464c483a9d68b5ea9e61021dda5d775797d4","tid":2378441,"uid":18477,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T12:59:41.000Z","msg":"賊嗌捉賊"},{"pid":"7dec651e5ca82fc7a90f59cce3afffe7c002b8ab","tid":2378441,"uid":16109,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T13:07:05.000Z","msg":"講就反腐實為權鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdd487ac8841539d769d8a2bba08f5a361359805","tid":2378441,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T13:07:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28288521a643843e2c59f1f4b3b05111f32f3eb0","tid":2378441,"uid":258903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T13:3